name: DOGU ACROBATS
description:
#02/07 of DOGU - White Series

The fabulous duo, the astounding Dogu Acrobats! Marvel at their talent. Stare in awe of their beauty! Watch their thrilling act! And if you're worried about the larger Dogu's neck - all is good, the little dude is a fully licensed chiropractor.

---

The White Series focuses on combining old nature pictures with the DOGUs. This is an introduction to their world. Kind of like postcards from their land.

This series consists of 6 DOGUs and one secret DOGU.
